@host = http://localhost:5246

### --- School Structure ---

### Get School Levels (to find IDs)
GET {{host}}/api/SchoolLevels
Accept: application/json

### Create School Grade
# Replace levelId with a valid one from above
POST {{host}}/api/SchoolGrades
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "levelId": 1,
  "name": "Test Grade"
}

### Get School Grades
GET {{host}}/api/SchoolGrades
Accept: application/json

### Create School Group
# Replace gradeId with a valid one from above
POST {{host}}/api/SchoolGroups
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "gradeId": 1,
  "name": "Test Group"
}

### Get School Groups
GET {{host}}/api/SchoolGroups
Accept: application/json


### --- Incident Types ---

### Get Incident Types (Old Endpoint)
GET {{host}}/api/Incidents/types
Accept: application/json

### Get Incident Types (New Controller)
GET {{host}}/api/IncidentTypes
Accept: application/json

### Create Incident Type
POST {{host}}/api/IncidentTypes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Late Arrival Test",
  "severity": "Leve",
  "description": "Created via API"
}


